description:
Elie Faure's four-volume &quot;History of Art,&quot; published in 1919-1921 in French and in 1921-1924 in English by Harper and Brothers, translated by Walter Pach. The books are in the public domain, available at the Internet Archive, as low-quality image scans. This is the emended text extracted from those files.

Vol. I - Ancient Art
Vol. II - Mediaeval Art
Vol. III - Renaissance Art
Vol. IV - Modern Art

